{
  "texts": [
    "This prevents the capture of cross-cutting relationships among CTs.A significant concern regards the classifier's ability to perform well on articles from websites beyond Snopes.",
    "This is due to differences in language and text formatting.",
    "Besides, the tree construction was limited due to the difficulty of detecting and scraping English articles and CTs, thus not providing an accurate representation of CTs in other languages or regions.",
    "Computational limitations prevented the use of more advanced algorithms, such as XLNet, or a broader grid search during classifier training.",
    "Furthermore, the model's robustness was limited since the articles used for training were scraped from only four selected fact-checking sites."
  ]
}